text:
```astro milav.com/src/components/BlogPost.astro
---
const { title, url, date } = Astro.props;
---

<li><a href={url}>{title}</a>{date}</li>
```

Make this component look nice.
I'll improve the styling and structure of the BlogPost component to make it look nicer.

<patch>
<title>Enhance BlogPost component styling</title>
<edit>
<path>milav.com/src/components/BlogPost.astro</path>
<description>Update the component to use better styling and structure for blog post listings</description>
<operation>update</operation>
<old_text>---
const { title, url, date } = Astro.props;
---

<li><a href={url}>{title}</a>{date}</li></old_text>
<new_text>---
const { title, url, date } = Astro.props;

// Format date if it's provided
const formattedDate = date ? new Date(date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
  year: 'numeric',
  month: 'long',
  day: 'numeric'
}) : null;
---

<li class="blog-post">
  <a href={url} class="blog-post-title">{title}</a>
  {formattedDate && <span class="blog-post-date">{formattedDate}</span>}
</li>

<style>
  .blog-post {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    list-style-type: none;
  }

  .blog-post:hover {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
  }

  .blog-post-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .blog-post-title:hover {
    color: #0077cc;
  }

  .blog-post-date {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style></new_text>
</edit>
</patch>
